Installation

# Install rvm if needed and follow prompts
gem install rvm

# Download the project
git clone git@github.com:thefreedompartnership/writersresidence_monitoring.git
cd writersresidence_monitoring

# Follow prompts from rvm to install the right ruby and create the gemset then
rvm gemset use 'writersresidence_monitoring'

# Install the depends
gem install bundler
bundle

# Run the tests
cucumber 

I love:
https://github.com/cayblood/cucumber-webrat-mechanize-example
from where this is completely stolen.
